This effect requires a depth light in the scene alongside it. A prefab is provided in the package in Resources/Prefabs.
Blur has the following styles available: Gaussian, Selective, Bloom, Bokeh, Frosted, Pixel Distort, Extrusion, Smear, Zoom Radial, and Other Goodies.
Border has the following styles available: Vertical Letterboxing, Horizontal Letterboxing, Box, Circular, Polygon, Eye, Anime, and Map.
Chromatic has the following styles available: RGB, HSV, Negativity, Radial, Layered, and Blur.
Frames has the following styles available: Pride, Trans, Music, Polaroid, Super Eight, Magazine, Filmdom, Neon, Comic, and Film Stripes.
Outline has the following styles available: Colour (Skinny), and Depth (Thick).
Overlay has the following styles available: Image Still, Image Animated, and Collage.

Transition has the following styles available: Slide, Spot In, Spot Out, Box In, Box Out, Tile Bounce, Tile Wave, Shutter, Radial Swipe, Radial Repeat, Dissolve, Jagged Swipe, Delayed, Hexagonal Tiles, Hexagonal Swipe, and Modelo In.
Triplanar has the following styles available: Still Image, Animated Image, Colour, and Cells.
Zoom has the following styles available: Screen, Centering, Fisheye, and Follow.

You are viewing a preview of all of the effects available in the full version of June. They aren't functional and don't have all of the settings available, but you can see what all is included to help you decide if June would be beneficial to you.
